description:
Pros: Special deal every Tuesdays mild or spicy chicken leg and thigh for $1.99!!! I usually get it every other Tuesday for lunch since its near my work. Chicken are usually right out of the fryer. Tender and crispy chicken!!! Very tasty and flavorful. Sometimes they make a mistake and they add an extra chicken to my order :) Gravy to their mash is delish! They have this jambalaya rice which goes well with the chicken. Oh and yeah don't forget the crispy fries (;

Cons: Long lines and place is tiny. They only have like somewhere around 4-8 seats. Staff are usually friendly but most customers are obnoxious, so the staff goes crazy most of the time! Sketchy area with a lot of bums.

It doesn't stop me from coming here though. I just don't pay attention, mind my own business, buy the chicken and leave as fast as I can lol
